      "content": "that makes sense. but some people argue that if the system is specifically designed to let a few powerful countries block everything, then maybe it's not really about \"geopolitical realities\" but just a flawed system that prioritizes certain nations over human rights. do historians see those critiques as legitimate or just as unrealistic?",
